title: Best Bits with Eddie: PART 1
itunes:title: Best Bits with Eddie: PART 1
description:
Eddie joins Morgan and they each share vacation stories and how they spent their time off. They talk about the food businesses they dream of having one day and their most fun celebrity interactions. Eddie shared what touring is like for the Raging Idiots and Morgan shared some Food Worlds and things she’s been watching lately.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
